{"tid":291810,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人識解夢？","createTime":"2017-06-21T00:54:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-21T01:37:59.000Z","uid":10966,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0c70370931f2816f607aecaa95d1063a812f72bf","tid":291810,"uid":10966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T00:54:48.000Z","msg":"我琴晚發左個惡夢，夢到我好努力喺網上揾緊資料做功課，屋出面有兩個學生妹勁危險又貪玩咁爬緊，佢地放手就會墮樓，但我冇勸佢地唔好再玩。咁夢入面個場景就係我屋企有兩間屋，我由屋A行到屋B(隔離屋 冇打通)，行出去個陣個兩個學生妹就咁岩墮樓，我見住個一刻想衝過去捉住佢地隻手，但已經趕唔切，佢地由20樓跌左落去。我喺夢入面因為太驚而冇睇到佢地跌落地面個一刻。然後我一直狂喊，喊到醒左，而我醒個陣仍然係喊既樣，不過冇眼淚。<br />\n<br />\n有冇人知道個夢反映緊啲咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n背景:現實中我都係學生"},{"pid":"ed0462372f10e9f810c4f211d9a8da54078725f3","tid":291810,"uid":40389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T00:57:33.000Z","msg":"乖啦 正正經經識返個女朋友啦"},{"pid":"29d93377494ffd37e602c0841f75e55d887adc49","tid":291810,"uid":10966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T01:00:45.000Z","msg":"我係絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46bafc87586a71e14080f9244b39dbb017a8f981","tid":291810,"uid":86893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T01:20:59.000Z","msg":"功課自己做啦"},{"pid":"6a6f29e42357514f77771c54b87a8cf7503d4708","tid":291810,"uid":67617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T01:22:33.000Z","msg":"反映你現實係deadline fighter?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55e43c9390725d0e915a816f0dddbb1c67c255d8","tid":291810,"uid":117310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T01:28:30.000Z","msg":"你壓力太大"},{"pid":"6ffc1ae17cfc0aa4828c07786d8e9b0b2148f0dc","tid":291810,"uid":32722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T01:30:19.000Z","msg":"你知道你有個問題發生左, 你好想去處理, 但又冇能力/時間<br />\n<br />\n但又好驚佢會自然爆煲"},{"pid":"b9e49b759546f7b